01:31.848 --> 01:40.186
goes. And I think we need to streamline titles some 
way and make them functional. And I suspect we

01:49.617 --> 02:03.398
probably ought to streamline the amount of tenure 
that people have in a given administrative post,

01:49.617 --> 02:03.398
even though it's comfortable for people. And I 
have a high regard for our administrators. I think

