I think every scientist needs some skills in 
addition to theory. Mine happens to be electron

07:17.061 --> 07:21.768
microscopy and x-ray diffraction and a few of 
those. You sound like a land grant person as

07:23.490 --> 07:29.059
compared to a theoretical university person. 
