07:33.245 --> 07:40.215
travel is really important and it's built well 
into my profession. And I think that, I don't know

07:40.651 --> 07:51.106
how it fits everybody, but I think a great many of us 
as scholars, we need to do a significant amount of

07:40.651 --> 07:51.106
traveling. How adequate have you found the 
library resources here when you needed?

08:01.300 --> 08:03.042
