focused area, and I have usually taken Sometimes

08:09.608 --> 08:12.914
as many as 12 journals, right now it's not that 
many. But I have my library, three different

08:14.016 --> 08:20.948
bookcases in a row in my office. And my group uses 
them more than any others. And the computer is

08:25.235 --> 08:28.320
helping us a lot in that regard. But I think we just, 
as I see it, we sort of gradually kept ahead of not

08:28.761 --> 08:35.652
being so good. Like the library that's been built 
on West Campus is a tremendous asset to us. But

08:41.863 --> 08:47.412
we've got to equip it with our journals and things. 
Just as we're doing that, we're merging into the

08:47.881 --> 08:56.013
electronic age of publishing, and we don't quite 
know how that's all going to come together. So I

08:56.033 --> 08:58.917
guess we have to run faster.

